{"tid":2258290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鱷王達利奧：中國將壓倒美國 　人民幣勢取代美元","createTime":"2020-10-26T02:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T00:46:04.000Z","uid":43785,"like":32,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"18d8ab48663064b6aadf6c76f172c8cebdcb42b6","tid":2258290,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"鱷王達利奧：中國將壓倒美國 　人民幣勢取代美元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8NfcSt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8NfcSt.jpg&h=3be3984d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全球最大對沖基金「橋水」創辦人達利奧(Ray Dalio)周六(24日)出席上海外灘金融峰會時表示，預計人民幣未來將取代美元，目前是中國對人民幣進行國際化，並發展金融中心的良機。<br />\n外媒引述達利奧表示，當前美國和美元仍然非常強勢，因為世界上大多數人都用美國印製的鈔票來購買商品，美國依然控制着清算體系，如果發生資本戰爭，就能切斷人們的資金流，這種影響力將在短期內保持，尤其是在市場上存在大量美元計價債務的時期。然而，從長遠來看，市場終會找到替代風險的方法，從而削減美元的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n達利奧預計，未來美元將逐漸被人民幣所取代，其觀點源自對近500年來的儲備貨幣帝國的研究，首先是荷蘭帝國和荷蘭盾被大英帝國和英鎊所取代，之後又被美帝國和美元取代，這二者又將逐漸被中國和人民幣取代。<br />\n他認為，目前是中國對人民幣進行國際化並發展金融中心的行動良機，隨着內地資本市場的開放，鑑於投資中國的強大基本面，中國將會獲得有利的資金流。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普如果輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國就玩完"},{"pid":"ab05036b176e4bcf039ad0800242a75bbaab2c7d","tid":2258290,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3456209dd1690d1f96bcc0964799cbfa78a267","tid":2258290,"uid":141668,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:31:14.000Z","msg":"你點取代的"},{"pid":"e6803ed0d7ae51a496d4aff39cb7555a0e124454","tid":2258290,"uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"哩條友不嬲舔共<br />\n同埋近年表現勁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959abcf037742b4cab7a40b1e21a80981da44d0f","tid":2258290,"uid":12628,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"自由對換都做唔到，點國際化"},{"pid":"9196deddd9322f22dca44a9f562f2b94b572eb0d","tid":2258290,"uid":335434,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"//達利奧預計，未來美元將逐漸被人民幣所取代，<strong><span class=\"red\">其觀點源自對近500年來的儲備貨幣帝國的研究，首先是荷蘭帝國和荷蘭盾被大英帝國和英鎊所取代，之後又被美帝國和美元取代</span></strong>，這二者又將逐漸被中國和人民幣取代。//<br />\n<br />\n當年嘅荷蘭盾, 英鎊同依家嘅美金成為主流交易貨幣 都有個特色就係可以自由兌換同自由流通 但支国冥幣唔好話国外就連国內都做唔到自由兌換同流通啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315d86e37ced704906f330b97f4278000398440d","tid":2258290,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"你點取代的"},{"pid":"c146f62eb2676b667c0b0d47bf180359f02b9d16","tid":2258290,"uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"The losses continue to pile up for hedge fund king Ray Dalio<br />\n<br />\nA turbulent market sent Bridgewater Associates' flagship Pure Alpha II fund<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\"> down 18.6% as of August</span></strong></span>, the hedge fund's worst performance in a decade.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fortune.com/2020/09/15/the-losses-continue-to-pile-up-for-hedge-fund-king-ray-dalio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2Fthe-losses-continue-to-pile-up-for-hedge-fund-king-ray-dalio%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=367bfe47\" target=\"_blank\">https://fortune.com/2020/09/15/the-losses-continue-to-pile-up-for-hedge-fund-king-ray-dalio/</a>"},{"pid":"4060b9d07622ce0ec14f73d0e15a72d797cf48e9","tid":2258290,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"你點影的"},{"pid":"370bcd7ea69101a58c344beaa0cc17dbe2e171cf","tid":2258290,"uid":58503,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9196deddd9322f22dca44a9f562f2b94b572eb0d","tid":2258290,"uid":335